                            <comment id="14973268" author="svenmeier" created="Sun, 25 Oct 2015 14:44:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d propose to add an additional specialization to UrlEncoder:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;see branch &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6010&quot; title=&quot;Downloading filenames containing &amp;#39;,&amp;#39; or &amp;#39;;&amp;#39; gives problems&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-6010&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-6010&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-url-encoder for an implementation of UrlEncoder.HEADER&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;UrlEncoder.FULL_PATH isn&apos;t used in Wicket any longer - to simplify things we should remove it in Wicket 8 and deprecate it in Wicket 7&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;we could rename UrlEncoder to something better, perhaps just URIEncoder, PercentEncoder or just Encoder?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14978101" author="laurenshop" created="Wed, 28 Oct 2015 09:55:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have tested your changes in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6010&quot; title=&quot;Downloading filenames containing &amp;#39;,&amp;#39; or &amp;#39;;&amp;#39; gives problems&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-6010&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-6010&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-url-encoder branch and they work fine. I&apos;m not sure about renaming the UrlEncoder. The term URL encoding is widely used. Percent encoding is the more official term however, maybe this is the best candidate.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
